data.description: Four plex right next to downtown Seattle and commuter dream a minute away from the freeway. Updates throughout with new insulation, double pain vinyl windows, ductless heating and cooling in each unit, and 20k new roof installed last year. Plenty of room for parking around the units as well as two covered parking spaces and two storage units for more income. Top unit has a beautiful view. All tenants have been long term tenants thus the under market value rents.
